            <title>[OPENJPA-1847] Use a single connection when generating schema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-1847</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SchemaTool obtains a new connection for each table it creates, then again for each index on each table, and again for each FK, and so on. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The impact of obtaining multiple connections can be reduced by using a connection pool but it&apos;s still quite noticeable when running our unit tests when the schema tool runs for each test method. &lt;/p&gt;

